{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make videocalling while driving a specific criminal offence",
        "additional_details": "I want this law change as my farther was killed by someone who was videocalling while driving and they only got a sentence of 30 months.\r\n \r\nThere are already offences for using a mobile phone while driving, but making videocalling while driving a specific criminal offence, with penalties in line with drink and drug driving, should help stop particularly dangerous behaviour.\r\n \r\nI want the Government to make these changes to protect us all from individuals who feel it\u2019s okay to videocall while driving, even when there may be a serious outcome.\r\n",
        "background": "The Government should make videocalling while driving a specific criminal offence, with penalties in line with those for drink and drug driving.",
